 ### Example requests for API Key endpoints
 
 ### 1. Generate a new API key
 POST http://localhost:3000/api-keys
 Content-Type: application/json
 Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
 X-Refresh-Token: YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
 
 {
   "name": "Production API Key",
   "expiresInDays": 90
 }
 
 ### 2. List all API keys for authenticated user
 GET http://localhost:3000/api-keys
 Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
 X-Refresh-Token: YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
 
 ### 3. Revoke an API key
 DELETE http://localhost:3000/api-keys/UNIQUE_ID_HERE
 Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
 X-Refresh-Token: YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
 
 ### 4. Use API key to access protected endpoint (example)
 GET http://localhost:3000/protected/resource
 X-API-Key: sk_live_YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
